Build dependencies\par
------------------\par
In order to compile this project the following libraries are required:  \par
- libzip2 (libzip-dev) and dependencies (zlib)\par
- Boost libraries (libboost-filesystem-dev)\par
\par
Compiling AirspaceConverter on Linux\par
------------------------------------\par
From the root of this project: `make all`  \par
To build in debug: `make DEBUG=1 all`  \par
The "AirspaceConverter" executable will be located in the "Release" or "Debug" folder\par
\par
Installing AirspaceConverter on Linux\par
------------------------------------\par
From the root of this project: `sudo make install`  \par
To uninstall: `sudo make uninstall` \par
\par
Compiling AirspaceConverter with MFC interface on Windows\par
---------------------------------------------------------\par
In the "VisualStudio" folder there is the VisualStudio solution and project files.\par
\par
Compiling the Qt executable\par
---------------------------\par
In the "AirspaceConverterQt" folder there is the Qt project, it needs the shared library libAirspaceConverter already compiled and installed for the same platform.\par
